### 1. Test Server Hidup
GET http://localhost:5173/

### 2. REGISTER USER BARU (Operator PPDB)
POST http://localhost:5173/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_ppdb",
  "password": "password123",
  "nama_lengkap": "Ustadz Admin",
  "peran": "operator_ppdb"
}

### 3. LOGIN (Coba masuk dengan akun tadi)
POST http://localhost:5173/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_ppdb",
  "password": "password123"
}

